<div class="article-body">
<p>Plumbing problems don't wait for a convenient time. A slow leak behind a wall can turn into thousands of dollars in mold damage before you ever notice it. A failing water heater can leave your family without hot water for days. That's why we treat every job — big or small — with the same urgency and precision.</p>
<p>At ReformaT Venezuela, our licensed plumbers handle everything from emergency repairs to full system overhauls across Valencia, San Diego, Carabobo, and Caracas. We carry the right parts, the right tools, and the right experience to solve your problem in one visit whenever possible.</p>
<img src="/images/fontaneria.webp" alt="Professional plumbing work by ReformaT Venezuela" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" />

<h2>What's Wrong with Your Plumbing?</h2>
<p>Most Venezuelan homes and buildings we inspect share the same handful of issues — problems that get worse (and more expensive) the longer they go unchecked:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Galvanized pipe corrosion:</strong> Those old metal pipes restrict water pressure, rust from the inside out, and eventually spring leaks. If your building is over 25 years old, you probably have them.</li>
<li><strong>Low water pressure:</strong> Usually caused by mineral buildup, partially closed shutoff valves, or undersized supply lines — not just "the city's problem."</li>
<li><strong>Recurring drain clogs:</strong> A plunger only buys time. Persistent slow drains point to grease, tree root intrusion, or a collapsed line that needs real attention.</li>
<li><strong>Hidden slab leaks:</strong> Unexplained spikes in your water bill, warm spots on the floor, or the sound of running water when every faucet is off — these are red flags.</li>
<li><strong>Outdated water heaters:</strong> Units past 10 years old lose efficiency fast, and they're one bad day away from flooding your utility room.</li>
</ul>

<h2>What We Actually Do</h2>
<p><strong>Leak Detection &amp; Repair:</strong> We use electronic detection equipment to pinpoint hidden leaks behind walls and under slabs — no guesswork, no tearing up your floors to "find" the problem.</p>
<p><strong>Pipe Replacement:</strong> We pull out corroded galvanized lines and run modern PEX or copper that won't rust, won't restrict flow, and comes with a manufacturer warranty.</p>
<p><strong>Drain Cleaning:</strong> Mechanical augers for standard blockages, hydro-jetting for stubborn grease and root intrusion. We clear it completely, not just enough to get you through the week.</p>
<p><strong>Water Heater Installation:</strong> Tank and tankless — gas and electric. We handle the venting, gas line connections, expansion tanks, and pressure relief valves so everything passes inspection.</p>
<p><strong>Fixture Installation:</strong> Faucets, toilets, showers, tubs, and specialty fixtures — all installed with proper sealing, supply line connections, and zero tolerance for drips.</p>

<h2>Bathroom &amp; Kitchen Plumbing</h2>
<p>Renovations almost always involve plumbing work. Moving a sink six feet sounds simple until you're routing new drain lines, extending supply runs, and making sure venting still works. We handle complete reconfigurations:</p>
<p><strong>Relocating Fixtures:</strong> Moving sinks, toilets, showers, and appliances to new locations with properly sloped drain extensions and balanced supply lines.</p>
<p><strong>Adding Fixtures:</strong> Installing a second bathroom, wet bar, or laundry hookup — with the venting, drainage, and water supply capacity to handle the added demand.</p>
<p><strong>Upgrading to Water-Efficient Models:</strong> Low-flow toilets (1.28 GPF), water-saving showerheads, and efficient faucets that cut your water bill without anyone noticing a difference in performance.</p>

<h2>Water Filtration &amp; Treatment</h2>
<p>Water quality varies a lot across Venezuela — from sediment-heavy municipal supply to hard water that destroys fixtures over time. We install filtration systems that make your water taste better, protect your plumbing, and keep your family healthier:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Whole-house filtration:</strong> Removes sediment, chlorine, and contaminants from every drop entering your property. One system, every faucet covered.</li>
<li><strong>Under-sink systems:</strong> Point-of-use filtration for drinking and cooking water — clean, great-tasting water right from the kitchen tap.</li>
<li><strong>UV purification:</strong> Ultraviolet treatment that neutralizes bacteria and viruses, especially important for properties on well water or areas with unreliable municipal supply.</li>
<li><strong>Water softening:</strong> Protects pipes, water heaters, dishwashers, and washing machines from mineral buildup that cuts equipment lifespan in half.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Why Homeowners Trust Us</h2>
<ul>
<li>Licensed, insured plumbers — not handymen with a pipe wrench</li>
<li>Upfront pricing before we start any work. You approve the quote, we do the job.</li>
<li>We carry common parts on our trucks so most repairs happen in a single visit</li>
<li>Every installation comes with a written warranty on parts and labor</li>
<li>We clean up after ourselves — you won't find pipe shavings or water spots when we leave</li>
<li>Emergency service available when things can't wait until Monday</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Got a plumbing problem?</strong> <a href="/en/contact">Get in touch today</a> for a free consultation and an honest, detailed quote — no pressure, no surprise charges.</p>
